<H3> <TI>   Kravchuk Position on Division of Bases </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kravchuk Position on Division of Bases </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94UM0418B Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 26 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 94UM0418B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA </F>
