<H3> <TI>   Afghan POW on Service With Azeribaijani Forces </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Afghan POW on Service With Azeribaijani Forces </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K1306A Yerevan GOLOS ARMENII in Russian 26 May 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 944K1306A </F>
