<H3> <TI>   Decree on Enterprises Involved in Foreign Military-Technical </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Decree on Enterprises Involved in Foreign Military-Technical </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Cooperation 

<F P=102>   94UM0435A Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 28 May 94 p 5 </F>
<F P=103> 94UM0435A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA </F>
