<H3> <TI>   Tunguska Air Defense System </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Tunguska Air Defense System </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94UM0438A Moscow TEKHNIKA I VOORUZHENIYE in Russian No 1-2, 
1994 pp 33-35 </F>

<F P=103> 94UM0438A </F>
