<H3> <TI>   Disposal of Unused Garrison Facilities </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Disposal of Unused Garrison Facilities </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94UM0432A Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 28 May 94 p 1 </F>
