<H3> <TI>   Insurgent Supply Dumps Found in Tajikistan </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Insurgent Supply Dumps Found in Tajikistan </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   94UM0437A Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA in Russian 2 Jun 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> 94UM0437A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KRASNAYA ZVEZDA </F>
